{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2452 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2452 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"pos":[598,618],"content":"Compiler Error C2452","linkify":"Compiler Error C2452","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2452","pos":[0,20]}]},{"content":"'type' : invalid source type for safe_cast","pos":[619,661]},{"content":"The source type for <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>safe_cast<ept id=\"p1\">](../../windows/safe-cast-cpp-component-extensions.md)</ept> was not valid.","pos":[668,767],"source":"The source type for [safe_cast](../../windows/safe-cast-cpp-component-extensions.md) was not valid."},{"content":"For example, all types in a <ph id=\"ph1\">`safe_cast`</ph> operation must be CLR types.","pos":[769,837],"source":"  For example, all types in a `safe_cast` operation must be CLR types."},{"content":"The following sample generates C2452:","pos":[844,881]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2452 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2452\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2452\"\nms.assetid: a4ec7642-6660-4c7a-9866-853d1cc67daf\ncaps.latest.revision: 10\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2452\n'type' : invalid source type for safe_cast  \n  \n The source type for [safe_cast](../../windows/safe-cast-cpp-component-extensions.md) was not valid.  For example, all types in a `safe_cast` operation must be CLR types.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2452:  \n  \n```  \n// C2452.cpp  \n// compile with: /clr  \n  \nstruct A {};  \nstruct B : public A {};  \n  \nref struct C {};  \nref struct D : public C{};  \n  \nint main() {  \n   A a;  \n   safe_cast<B*>(&a);   // C2452  \n  \n   // OK  \n   C ^ c = gcnew C;  \n   safe_cast<D^>(c);  \n}  \n```"}